            "content": "RESTful API",
            "level": 2
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "column": 1,
            "order": 2,
            "content": "IntraVox provides a **RESTful API** for programmatic access:\n\n• List, create, update, delete pages\n• Manage navigation structure\n• Query page content\n• Update widgets and layouts\n• Manage permissions"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "column": 2,
            "order": 1,
            "content": "Authentication",
            "level": 2
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "column": 2,
            "order": 2,
            "content": "API requests use **Nextcloud authentication**:\n\n• App passwords for user accounts\n• OAuth2 for external applications\n• Session-based for same-origin requests\n• Rate limiting and security headers"
          }
        ]
      },
